    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in showroom condition\u2014I've babied it from day one! There isn't a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for something that's been meticulously cared for and loved, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
