    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 chassis, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag six-speed manual and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle underwent preventative subframe reinforcement and retains its original factory tolerances. The suspension maintains peak damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection, and the engine bay remains in a concours-clean state. This is a mechanically impeccable, turn-key investment for the serious driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
